a pedirle matrimonio.]

00:40:51.630 --> 00:40:52.630
[Como muestra de sinceridad]

00:40:53.320 --> 00:40:55.630
[talló a mano
la flor de loto de pan de oro]

00:40:56.110 --> 00:40:57.630
[y cada uno guarda una mitad]

00:40:58.110 --> 00:40:59.550
[como prenda de amor.]

00:41:03.360 --> 00:41:06.230
